				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1nh-H%E1%BA%A1o-Nhi%C3%AAn/%C4%90%C4%83ng-T%E1%BB%95ng-Tr%C3%AC-t%E1%BB%B1-ph%C3%B9-%C4%91%E1%BB%93/poem-ktoTWoyv3rrUbCBf7nZmpw">Đăng Tổng Trì tự phù đồ - 登總持寺浮圖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1nh-H%E1%BA%A1o-Nhi%C3%AAn/author-ep8IiRc7UH2qX75S-LVnLw">Mạnh Hạo Nhiên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-Tuy%C3%AAn-Ch%C3%A2u-Khai-Nguy%C3%AAn-t%E1%BB%B1-t%E1%BB%B1-tr%C3%AD-%C6%B0-%C4%90%C3%B4ng-T%E1%BA%A5n-th%C3%AC/poem-vD7r3eBbK0uI4eWOqyY6ew">Đề Tuyên Châu Khai Nguyên tự, tự trí ư Đông Tấn thì - 題宣州開元寺，寺置於東晉時</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/author-3vzgm_fq7JLuFBSuENsFJw">Đỗ Mục</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Huy-Tr%E1%BB%A9/L%E1%BB%AF-x%C3%A1-c%E1%BA%A3m-thu%E1%BA%ADt-t%E1%BA%ADp-c%E1%BB%95/poem-4xtLcuc_vsSiYWQMqL_JfQ">Lữ xá cảm thuật (tập cổ) - 旅舍感述 （集古）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Huy-Tr%E1%BB%A9/author-l-vfhV6KqRexQyEkpib8Ng">Đặng Huy Trứ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-Trung-H%C3%A0nh/S%C6%A1n-L%C4%83ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-trung-phong-v%C5%A9/poem-gD0FrXD6P5xRUsqPInUdkQ">Sơn Lăng đạo trung phong vũ - 山陵道中風雨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-Trung-H%C3%A0nh/author-aUZNU7wtOFuw7SBMW9XW1Q">Từ Trung Hành</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%A3o-Chi%E1%BA%BFu/T%E1%BA%B7ng-Ph%C3%B3-%C4%91%C3%B4-t%C3%A0o-bi%E1%BB%87t/poem-6D8DRnbPOONMJ341dyakBA">Tặng Phó đô tào biệt - 贈傅都曹別</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%A3o-Chi%E1%BA%BFu/author-5adVbUFDYBOaWjhVfsxMBA">Bão Chiếu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/T%E1%BB%8Bch-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-l%C3%A2u/poem-ZW2VVC-5DvC0yt-mqNC-pw">Tịch Dương lâu - 夕陽樓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/T%C3%ADch-hoa-b%E1%BB%99-T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ch%C3%A2u-T%C3%A0ng-Xu%C3%A2n-vi%C3%AAn-ch%E1%BB%A7-nh%C3%A2n-nguy%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%ADn-k%E1%BB%B3-4/poem-S6C3Yi81DyJSK-jCA8DKcw">Tích hoa bộ Tương Châu Tàng Xuân viên chủ nhân nguyên vận kỳ 4 - 惜花步藏湘州春園主人元韻其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/author-TXAaCmjdRWIV6MkCYE1psQ">Lỗ Tấn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%C6%B0/poem-WQkvak0bO6BDMarTsB2kng">Trường tương tư - 長相思</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/author-Rh6zapU4AwLAuhG1Xl_FMw">Âu Dương Tu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C4%83ng-Qu%E1%BB%91c-Phi%C3%AAn/%E1%BB%A8c-%C4%91%E1%BB%87/poem-ShqMOyHAaPzqXVv_NTktug">Ức đệ - 憶弟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C4%83ng-Qu%E1%BB%91c-Phi%C3%AAn/author-nwGIjF6JjQC812vXoHUn9A">Tăng Quốc Phiên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu-Th%E1%BA%BF-Nam/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-phong/poem-B1UEqLELMIBBPje7-TEs7Q">Vịnh phong - 詠風</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu-Th%E1%BA%BF-Nam/author-aJYwx1rKXLDSeCfh-ncxCw">Ngu Thế Nam</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
